{
    "title": "sigusr1 and sigusr2",
    "html": "<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\"><h3 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"46\"><strong data-start=\"4\" data-end=\"44\">SIGUSR1 vs. SIGUSR2 in Linux Signals</strong></h3>\n<p data-start=\"48\" data-end=\"273\"><strong data-start=\"48\" data-end=\"61\"><code data-start=\"50\" data-end=\"59\">SIGUSR1</code></strong> and <strong data-start=\"66\" data-end=\"79\"><code data-start=\"68\" data-end=\"77\">SIGUSR2</code></strong> are <strong data-start=\"84\" data-end=\"108\">user-defined signals</strong> in Linux/Unix that <strong data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"172\">applications can use for custom purposes</strong>. Unlike other signals (like <code data-start=\"201\" data-end=\"210\">SIGKILL</code> or <code data-start=\"214\" data-end=\"223\">SIGTERM</code>), these do not have predefined system behavior.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"278\">\n<h2 data-start=\"280\" data-end=\"304\"><strong data-start=\"283\" data-end=\"302\">1. What They Do</strong></h2>\n<ul data-start=\"305\" data-end=\"456\">\n<li data-start=\"305\" data-end=\"376\"><strong data-start=\"307\" data-end=\"332\"><code data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"318\">SIGUSR1</code> (Signal 10)</strong> â†’ Custom signal for user-defined actions.</li>\n<li data-start=\"377\" data-end=\"456\"><strong data-start=\"379\" data-end=\"404\"><code data-start=\"381\" data-end=\"390\">SIGUSR2</code> (Signal 12)</strong> â†’ Another custom signal, separate from <code data-start=\"444\" data-end=\"453\">SIGUSR1</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"458\" data-end=\"584\">These signals are <strong data-start=\"476\" data-end=\"507\">not generated by the system</strong>. Instead, they are <strong data-start=\"527\" data-end=\"544\">sent manually</strong> by the user or another program using:</p>\n<pre class=\"!overflow-visible\" data-start=\"585\" data-end=\"636\"><div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-gray-950\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-[5px] h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none\">sh</div><div class=\"sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center rounded bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\"><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1\" aria-label=\"Copy\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg>Copy</button></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"flex select-none items-center gap-1\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\"><path d=\"M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378 6.10476 20.3159L8.97693 19.8372C9.72813 19.712 10.1037 19.6494 10.4542 19.521C10.7652 19.407 11.0608 19.2549 11.3343 19.068C11.6425 18.8575 11.9118 18.5882 12.4503 18.0497L20 10.5C21.3807 9.11929 21.3807 6.88071 20 5.5C18.6193 4.11929 16.3807 4.11929 15 5.5L7.45026 13.0497C6.91175 13.5882 6.6425 13.8575 6.43197 14.1657C6.24513 14.4392 6.09299 14.7348 5.97903 15.0458C5.85062 15.3963 5.78802 15.7719 5.66282 16.5231Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M14.5 7L18.5 11\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Edit</button></span></div></div></div><div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"!whitespace-pre language-sh\"><span><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">kill</span> -SIGUSR1 &lt;PID&gt;  \n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">kill</span> -SIGUSR2 &lt;PID&gt;\n</span></code></div></div></pre>\n<p data-start=\"637\" data-end=\"639\">or</p>\n<pre class=\"!overflow-visible\" data-start=\"640\" data-end=\"701\"><div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-gray-950\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-[5px] h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none\">sh</div><div class=\"sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center rounded bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\"><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1\" aria-label=\"Copy\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg>Copy</button></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"flex select-none items-center gap-1\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\"><path d=\"M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378 6.10476 20.3159L8.97693 19.8372C9.72813 19.712 10.1037 19.6494 10.4542 19.521C10.7652 19.407 11.0608 19.2549 11.3343 19.068C11.6425 18.8575 11.9118 18.5882 12.4503 18.0497L20 10.5C21.3807 9.11929 21.3807 6.88071 20 5.5C18.6193 4.11929 16.3807 4.11929 15 5.5L7.45026 13.0497C6.91175 13.5882 6.6425 13.8575 6.43197 14.1657C6.24513 14.4392 6.09299 14.7348 5.97903 15.0458C5.85062 15.3963 5.78802 15.7719 5.66282 16.5231Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M14.5 7L18.5 11\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Edit</button></span></div></div></div><div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"!whitespace-pre language-sh\"><span><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">kill</span> -10 &lt;PID&gt;  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># SIGUSR1</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">kill</span> -12 &lt;PID&gt;  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># SIGUSR2</span>\n</span></code></div></div></pre>\n<hr data-start=\"703\" data-end=\"706\">\n<h2 data-start=\"708\" data-end=\"756\"><strong data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"756\">2. Difference Between SIGUSR1 and SIGUSR2</strong></h2>\n<table data-start=\"757\" data-end=\"1227\"><thead data-start=\"757\" data-end=\"789\"><tr data-start=\"757\" data-end=\"789\"><th data-start=\"757\" data-end=\"768\">Feature</th><th data-start=\"768\" data-end=\"778\">SIGUSR1</th><th data-start=\"778\" data-end=\"789\">SIGUSR2</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"821\" data-end=\"1227\"><tr data-start=\"821\" data-end=\"902\"><td><strong data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"834\">Purpose</strong></td><td>User-defined (Custom action 1)</td><td>User-defined (Custom action 2)</td></tr><tr data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"995\"><td><strong data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"925\">Default Behavior</strong></td><td>Terminates process if unhandled</td><td>Terminates process if unhandled</td></tr><tr data-start=\"996\" data-end=\"1042\"><td><strong data-start=\"998\" data-end=\"1030\">Signal Number (Most Systems)</strong></td><td>10</td><td>12</td></tr><tr data-start=\"1043\" data-end=\"1227\"><td><strong data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1057\">Use Case</strong></td><td>Often used for reloading config files, logging, debugging, etc.</td><td>Another user-defined action, can be used for different operations like toggling modes, backup, etc.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<ul data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1435\">\n<li data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1303\">Since they are user-defined, developers <strong data-start=\"1271\" data-end=\"1300\">decide how to handle them</strong>.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1304\" data-end=\"1435\">Some applications use <strong data-start=\"1328\" data-end=\"1383\"><code data-start=\"1330\" data-end=\"1339\">SIGUSR1</code> for one purpose (e.g., reloading configs)</strong> and <strong data-start=\"1388\" data-end=\"1433\"><code data-start=\"1390\" data-end=\"1399\">SIGUSR2</code> for another (e.g., debug logs).</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1437\" data-end=\"1440\">\n<h2 data-start=\"1442\" data-end=\"1464\"><strong data-start=\"1445\" data-end=\"1464\">3. Example in C</strong></h2>\n<h3 data-start=\"1465\" data-end=\"1505\"><strong data-start=\"1469\" data-end=\"1505\">Handling <code data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1489\">SIGUSR1</code> and <code data-start=\"1494\" data-end=\"1503\">SIGUSR2</code></strong></h3>\n<p data-start=\"1506\" data-end=\"1590\">Hereâ€™s a C program that catches and reacts differently to <code data-start=\"1564\" data-end=\"1573\">SIGUSR1</code> and <code data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1587\">SIGUSR2</code>:</p>\n<pre class=\"!overflow-visible\" data-start=\"1592\" data-end=\"2239\"><div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-gray-950\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-[5px] h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none\">c</div><div class=\"sticky top-9 md:top-[5.75rem]\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-2 flex h-9 items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center rounded bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary px-2 font-sans text-xs text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\"><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1\" aria-label=\"Copy\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg>Copy</button></span><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"flex select-none items-center gap-1\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\"><path d=\"M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378 6.10476 20.3159L8.97693 19.8372C9.72813 19.712 10.1037 19.6494 10.4542 19.521C10.7652 19.407 11.0608 19.2549 11.3343 19.068C11.6425 18.8575 11.9118 18.5882 12.4503 18.0497L20 10.5C21.3807 9.11929 21.3807 6.88071 20 5.5C18.6193 4.11929 16.3807 4.11929 15 5.5L7.45026 13.0497C6.91175 13.5882 6.6425 13.8575 6.43197 14.1657C6.24513 14.4392 6.09299 14.7348 5.97903 15.0458C5.85062 15.3963 5.78802 15.7719 5.66282 16.5231Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M14.5 7L18.5 11\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Edit</button></span></div></div></div><div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"!whitespace-pre language-c\"><span><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">#<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">#<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;signal.h&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">#<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;unistd.h&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Signal handler function</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-type\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">signal_handler</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> sig)</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (sig == SIGUSR1) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Received SIGUSR1: Performing action 1...\\n\"</span>);\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (sig == SIGUSR2) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Received SIGUSR2: Performing action 2...\\n\"</span>);\n    }\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">main</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Register signal handlers</span>\n    signal(SIGUSR1, signal_handler);\n    signal(SIGUSR2, signal_handler);\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Process ID: %d\\n\"</span>, getpid());\n    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Waiting for signals...\\n\"</span>);\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Infinite loop to keep the program running</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> (<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        sleep(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>);\n    }\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n}\n</span></code></div></div></pre>\n<h3 data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2268\"><strong data-start=\"2245\" data-end=\"2268\">Running the Program</strong></h3>\n<ol data-start=\"2269\" data-end=\"2630\">\n<li data-start=\"2269\" data-end=\"2359\">Compile and run:\n<pre class=\"!overflow-visible\" data-start=\"2294\" data-end=\"2359\"><div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-toke